Fully Renovated (Top to Bottom) 2 Family Home, Brand New Stucco Exterior. 3 Bedroom Over 2 Bedroom Over A Full High Ceiling Finished Basement. All New Hardwood Floors, Electric, Plumbing, Wiring, Electric, Heating, Windows, Washer & Dryer Hookups. High Ceiling, Lots of High Hat Lighting. CLOSE TO SCHOOLS, SHOPPING, RESTAURANTS & TRANSPORTATION!  ~ONLY 3.5% DOWN!~ ~FHA APPROVED!~ ~FIRST TIME HOME BUYER’S PROGRAM AVAILABLE!~ ~LOWEST INTEREST RATES FINANCING AVAILABLE!~ __Visit http://www.TopLevelProperties.com For More Homes!__
